    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Il <rs key="#Priests">prete</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Teobaldus">Tetbaldo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Clerical_concubinage">figlio della <persName
                                key="#Clerical_concubinage">fu <name ref="Rodelinda/Rotia">Rodilinda
                                    detta Rozia</name></persName></rs>, vende ai fratelli
                                <persName><name ref="Eritius/Venerandus">Erizio detto
                                Venerando</name></persName> e <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Pietro</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Petrus"
                                >Pietro</name></persName> un appezzamento di terra, cum cassina
                        super se abentes, posto in loco et finibus <placeName ref="#places/23"
                            >Catiana</placeName> ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Petiae #Fiscal_property #Mention #Emperor/king #Queen"
                            ref="#places/23"><rs key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Mention">Curte</rs>
                            <rs key="#Queen">Regine</rs></placeName> quas mihi per cartule scripte
                        sunt manibus Heriberti notarii domni imperatoris <rs key="#Venditio">ex
                            conparationem</rs> obvenit da <persName><name ref="Albo"
                            >Albone</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Teobaldus/Teutius"
                                >Tetbaldo detto Teuzio</name></persName> e dalla moglie
                                <persName><name ref="Bonitia">Bonizia</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Rotius/Omicius">Rozio detto
                            Omicio</name></persName>, <rs key="#Confinia">confinante</rs> ambas
                        capitas in via publica, lato uno con <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Fiscal_property #Mention">terra</rs> del <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">re</rs>, alio lato con terra dei suddetti fratelli,
                        con tutte le sue dipendenze et cum exempler de suprascripte cartule, per il
                        prezzo di 15 soldi d'argento. Chiede al <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notaio
                            imperiale</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Eribertus"
                            >Eriberto</name></persName> la stesura della cartula. Actum in loco ubi
                        dicitur <placeName ref="#places/62">Bibbia</placeName> prope <rs
                            key="#Castle">castello</rs> et <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/72"><rs key="#Churches">eclesia</rs> Sancte
                            Marie ubi dicitur <placeName key="#Castle #Churches" ref="#places/63">
                                ad Monte</placeName></orgName>. <rs key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs>
                        sottoscrittori: <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Rotius"
                            >Rozio</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Rotius/Omicius"
                                >Rozio detto Omicio</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrando</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Rodulfus">Rodolfo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodolfo</name></persName> del
                            <persName>fu <name ref="Alboinus">Albuino</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
